{% set name = "ispc" %}

package:

  version: {{ version }}

    - flex      # [unix]
    - bison     # [unix]
    - m2-flex   # [win]

    - clang     {{ llvm_version }}.*  # [unix]

    - llvmdev   {{ llvm_version }}.*

    - clangdev  {{ llvm_version }}.*
    - llvmdev   {{ llvm_version }}.*

    - zlib

test:
  commands:
    - ispc --help

about:

  license: BSD-3-Clause
  license_file: LICENSE.txt
